text: John Kevin Paul Keegan (born 5 August 1981) is an English former professional footballer who played as a defender in the Football League for York City, and in non-League football for Scarborough. and Chester City F.C. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Footballers from Liverpool Category:English footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:York City F.C. players Category:Scarborough F.C. players Category:English Football League players Category:National League (English football) players
